\par unit PropEdit
\par 
\par TObject
\par 
\par TPropertyEditor class represents editor for TProperty object. 
\par To create new property editor class create new descendant from TPropertyEditor and override Execute method using Prop property that contains the edited property.
\par 
\par PropEdit unit defines TPropertyEditorClass as 
\par TPropertyEditorClass = class of TPropertyEditor;
\par This type is used in GetEditorClass function and OnGetEditorClass event of TObjectInspector.
