\par This constructor creates and initializes TPropertyEditor instance.
\par 
\par function Execute: Boolean; virtual; abstract;
\par This fu
nction must call editor and sets property value using Prop property if the changes must be applied. This is abstract function, so it must be overridden in the descendant classes. This function must return True if the value is changed otherwise False.

